{"tid":697953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 愛國阿伯披五星旗　譚Sir訓斥","createTime":"2018-06-11T09:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T10:29:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc828b4ee8ad096b34c575452511d95086d3105","tid":697953,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20417015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20417015&d=YagISGyFobxopJgWThF5%2FiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a3654bbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20417015&h=6e24b4e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180611/20417015</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n愛國阿伯披五星旗　譚Sir訓斥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a09a04a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa09a04a.gif&h=9dde7e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■愛國阿伯身披五星紅旗同建制派合照，點知在場人士唔多like。黎樹雄攝 <br />\n <br />\n講開高永文同植潔鈴拉票，其實建制派噚日總動員幫植拉票，更有唔少建制派支持者到場幫佢打氣，但係唔係個個都受歡迎，好似平日逢周二早上，都會去行政會議示威區展示國旗嘅中醫師，今次佢去撐植潔鈴，竟然俾民記譚耀宗「訓斥」佢，真係估唔到。<br />\n<br />\n話說呢名中醫師原來係東區選民，今次東區補選佢話自己有投票，仲投咗畀植潔鈴，而佢噚日身披國旗行過植拉票檔口，已經表現得好high，一度走埋去同工聯會王國興握手。<br />\n<br />\n但因為佢披住國旗，當佢走去同建制派合照時，在場嘅「譚Sir」譚耀宗就表現得十分抗拒，仲出埋口叫佢唔好攞支國旗咁玩！之後譚直情用手推開佢㖭！譚Sir咁嘅反應自然令佢好無癮，惟有一個人離開。  <br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 助選變主角　民望高人氣贏阿舜 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (尊子)"},{"pid":"d67c2cb2139a6514ef3eeb772c06755f30361de2","tid":697953,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"打完J唔要咸相<br />\n正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f894c64869b50e2c4ac8f760349368be487a536","tid":697953,"uid":13115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353cafd672284cb10bf9d5c2c05b9446ef90b16e","tid":697953,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"阿伯你都就快入棺材，企開啲啦屌你老母。"},{"pid":"9a0fd085e7e710287fed4534ddf416ed02fd0d4f","tid":697953,"uid":56453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"國旗當披肩<br />\n幾時告埋個老嘢？"}]}